The paper proposes the concept of "science bots" that autonomously perform programmed tasks on input data and immediately publish the results. This involves the use of computational approaches and the acceleration of science, which are key themes in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cybernetics (cs.CY), deep learning (cs.DL), machine learning (cs.LG), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
